heading: Share Prakarsh
subHeading: Be a part in making Prakarsh XIII (2018) a success!
shareContent: PRAKARSH, a national level technical symposium to bring together the best brains in the country and give them a chance to showcase their skills and talents. This will give a platform for the students to interact and compete with each other. There are non-technical events too to incorporate fun activities alongside the technical fervour followed by Pro-nights. #Prakarsh2018
